node.text:
Say hello to Nigel, the crocodile.¹
📸: @from.miles.away

¹ Matt Deakin (@from.miles.away) recounts his experience capturing this moment: “This time last year, I was filming Nigel (the crocodile) in the creek, patiently tracking his movements in the shallows, when I was lucky enough to see and capture this moment when he swam over and scared a stingray on his way back home to his channel.”
Ayyy el drilococo, cree que no lo vi
ഒരെണ്ണം കിട്ടിക്കഴിയുമ്പോളും ഈ കിടപ്പ് തന്നെ കിടക്കണം
“this one is for my mate Steve”
